  "title": "ADMIN ASSISTANT",
  "description": "<p>Job Duties :</p><ul><li>Provide clerical and administrative support</li><li>To do procurement and purchasing</li><li>Support the project team in purchasing in materials, equipment and services required for on going projects</li><li>Carry out administrative duties such as filling, scanning documents, and compilation of reports/files</li><li>Perform any other ad-hoc duties as assigned</li></ul><p>Job Requirements :</p><ul><li>At least 1year of experience in an administration role</li><li>Self-motivated and able to work independently and under pressure</li><li>Flexible/adaptable with work assignment and ability to multitask</li><li>Positive work attitude, Meticulous and able to adhere to procedures and instructions well</li><li>Able to start work in short notice</li></ul>",
